data.value:
This app is a free open-source project by Lukas Langrock under the MIT license which means there is no warranty provided and I shall not be held liable for any kind of damage! After all you may lose unsaved work or mess up another running application. Use this with caution and common sense!
The application is built to be reliable and should accurately measure and count time. I can't exactly guarantee this but I aim to get the application to be as stable and polished as possible. In the case you encounter an error or notice the application not working as it should, an issue on GitHub or an Email would be very appreciated so I can fix the mistake.
If you enjoy using this free app, please consider writing a review on the Microsoft Store or starring the project on GitHub. Any contributions in the form of issues and PR's are very welcome. If you don't have a GitHub account, you can also write me an Email.
